==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Paned
<hw>Paned</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Having
panes; provided with panes; also, having openings; <as>as, a
<ex>paned</ex> window; <ex>paned</ex> window sash.</as></def>
⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Paned</xex> hose.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Massinger.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Mach.)</fld> <def>Having flat sides or surfaces;
<as>as, a six-<ex>paned</ex> nut</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Panegyric</ent>⟦br⟧
